'''Jahongir Oʻrozov''' ([[Cyrillic|Uzbek Cyrillic]]: Жаҳонгир Ўрозов; born 18 January 2004) is an Uzbek professional footballer who plays as a [[left-back]] for [[Dinamo Samarqand]] and the [[Uzbekistan national football team|Uzbekistan national team]].

==Club career==
Urozov began his senior career with [[Bunyodkor]] in 2022.

==International career==
Urozov made his debut for the [[Uzbekistan national football team|Uzbekistan]] main team on 27 March 2026 in a [[FIFA Series]] match against [[Gabon national football team|Gabon]].<ref>[https://www.soccerway.com/match/gabon-YJL8W78U/uzbekistan-EZYKKRMc/?mid=KbRpfX7I Uzbekistan 3–1 Gabon]</ref>

